results.title: Nursery decor. When The Red, Red Robin LYRICS print. With PERSONALISED MESSAGE. Rugby anthem, Nursery rhyme, Childs bedroom, Motivational
results.description:
ITEM DETAILS & ORDERING INFO
----------------------------------------------
- PRINTED items are full bleed (ink to the edge of the paper). Printed on 200gsm photo quality paper using a professional inkjet printer, then placed in a protective cellophane sleeve. Posted by Royal Mail First Class post.
- FRAMED items are available in white or black frames, in print sizes A4 and A3 (See size guide below). Posted by Royal Mail 2nd Class ‘Signed For’ post.
- DIGITAL FILE items are emailed via the Etsy ‘MESSAGES’ system, as high resolution JPG and PDF files, which the buyer is required to download and print themselves.

ORDERING FROM OUTSIDE THE UK
For those living outside the UK, DIGITAL FILES can be ordered using the following link:-
https://www.etsy.com/uk/listing/269234513/overseas-digital-file-order-for-a?ref=shop_home_active_1

HOW TO ORDER
1 - CHOOSE: Your size/product format (DIGITAL FILE, PRINT or FRAMED PRINT) from the ‘Size’ drop down menu.
2 - CHOOSE: Background colour from the ‘Primary colour’ drop down menu. The design/wording will be in white unless the ‘TWO COLOUR DESIGN’ option is selected (see below for more info).
3 - PERSONALISE: Provide your recipient’s name(s), date or special message in the ‘personalisation’ box. If one isn’t required state NONE, then only the artist name and song title will be printed. (PLEASE CHECK ALL OF YOUR WORDING & SPELLING CAREFULLY!)
4 - TWO COLOUR DESIGN: This option is for customers who’d like their design/wording in a second colour. Please state your choice of 2 colours and in which order in either the ‘personalisation’ box or ‘Add a note to TheDaisyHillShop’ at the checkout.
5 - For A3 and framed prints, ideally please provide an address where there will be SOMEONE AVAILABLE TO SIGN for your delivery. If someone is not available, a Royal Mail calling card will be left for you to either rearrange delivery, or collect from your local Royal Mail sorting office.

SIZE GUIDE
Please use the following measurements to help you select the correct frame size for your print. The DESIGN SIZE measurements are approximate dimensions which the design/wording takes up. All prints are full bleed (ink to the edge of the paper) and will fit the relevant ‘A’ sized frame.
- A5: PAPER SIZE 14.8x21cm - DESIGN SIZE 11x16cm - Fits a 5x7” picture area/window mount. (An excellent fit for the IKEA 21x30cm RIBBA frame, when used with the mount).
- A4: PAPER SIZE 21x29.7cm - DESIGN SIZE 16x23cm - Fits an 8x10” picture area/window mount. (An excellent fit for the IKEA 30x40cm RIBBA frame, when used with the mount).
- A3: PAPER SIZE 29.7x42cm - DESIGN SIZE 24x35cm - Fits an 11x16” picture area/window mount (An excellent fit for the IKEA 40x50cm RIBBA frame when used with the mount).
- A4 FRAME SIZE: 32.5x42.5cm*, with mount, ready to hang.
- A3 FRAME SIZE: 32.5x42.5cm*, NO MOUNT (print to frame edges), ready to hang. 

PLEASE NOTE
*Frame sizes are approximate. On occasion the stated frame sizes may become unavailable. At such times a suitable alternative, of a similar size, will be provided.

- For estimated delivery times, please read ‘Shipping & Policies’ section.
- The lyrics CAN NOT be customised! The design shown on the shop image, is the one you will receive. Please feel free to message me new song requests.
- Printed colours may differ slightly from the ones shown on screen, due to different monitor settings.
- FREE MAINLAND UK delivery only
